{"tid":1447430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 一齊幫手諗下記者會問咩問題問到警察一棟都無","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:28.000Z","uid":34355,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"26eec8f70402a421fdb381c6d48cb600f240b465","tid":1447430,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"記者聽日既問題絕對可以憾動到今日警察既所作所為，包括:<br />\n1. 室內放催淚彈<br />\n2. 布袋彈射眼球<br />\n3. 扮示威者<br />\n4. 北角紅衫福建幫打人警察完全無撚用<br />\n5. 繼續針對721元朗事件<br />\n<br />\n以上既五件事唔單止可以幫記者係警察記者會問更加針對既問題，仲可以令日後既民間記者會有更有力既理據質疑警察既行動有冇問題，迫使政府妥協促成獨立調查委員會，還義士一個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望集各位巴絲打既腦力去諗針對性既問題，問到班狗一棟都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係我所諗到既白痴問題:<br />\n1. 警方到底有冇依照武器廠商既指示去使用武器?如果無，點證明到警方係使用緊合理武力?<br />\n2. 橡膠子彈/布袋彈係射示威者四肢以令其行動不便，警方有冇需要為射到示威者眼球以導致其失明以負責?<br />\n3. (a.)(針對政府)政府一直以反對暴力為首，今次既過程入面證實到有警察扮示威者，點先証明到掟磚扔汽油彈係示威者自發而唔係警方誘使示威者使用?<br />\n3. (b.)點解扮示威者既警員唔需要展示委任證?<br />\n4. 可唔可以解答一下北角事件?(哩個靠各巴絲諗，應該有好大發揮空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n5. 721事件(如舊，咬撚住唔放<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n今日令到勇武大傷元氣，希望和理非及文宣巴絲幫手煲大今日既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"0bf8ce70af3e7f9cb65e90bcd844c91f7969e94f","tid":1447430,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:59:05.000Z","msg":"聽日要咬撚住班狗唔放呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d84ff9b1d9365c808482b36e94afa1f722768d","tid":1447430,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:04:09.000Z","msg":"推，幫下勇武手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ae0c4d44019b5626ec9a8fffbe3f498ade5d46","tid":1447430,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"太古站近距離開槍 <br />\n推市民落電梯"},{"pid":"c39ed3de602ef04fa5e63cbbc0b485c0cddaad4d","tid":1447430,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26ae0c4d44019b5626ec9a8fffbe3f498ade5d46","tid":1447430,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"太古站近距離開槍 <br />\n推市民落電梯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:27.000Z","msg":"推市民落電梯又係可以煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你老味成班狗係地鐵亂鳩咁扑"},{"pid":"7c79a72aedba221c0b730e94a306fd2b4c94be78","tid":1447430,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"一個人腦諗到既野真係唔多，幫下手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7cba32812198df4f0e94b46be2f686fa4d44dc","tid":1447430,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:22.000Z","msg":"如何投訴無編號、無委任證，一米內掃射示威者頭部既警員"},{"pid":"e9c6aac450b1f0dc0dd962fa300568c5c6f10714","tid":1447430,"uid":146556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"對記者會無expectation"},{"pid":"1e4e41fbcec50877dffdde958da3041f5a2c3cc7","tid":1447430,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:01.000Z","msg":"警犬發言人：你問東咪我答西"},{"pid":"c690dee94e108e9277bfd6ea95acf4738dc57106","tid":1447430,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"警方插贜嫁禍依個手法有幾常用？"},{"pid":"368fb02e020afb6feb5454cabdb7ca78a47a83e9","tid":1447430,"uid":34355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:58.000Z","msg":"比埋片班記者睇，開鎗個件仲要速龍黎，警察守則去左邊?<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/c67rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fc67rs&d=6